@node introduction
                                                                 .

                                                                 :
                                                                 :
             __________________.______.      ________            :
          ._(___)_.   ___     _|      l_____\\_     /____________:_ _
          |       |----/      \        /     \   __/\      __    :
          l_______|   /_______/        |-----/_______\____       :
                              l________|(rLf)            /-------:-
                                                                 :
                                                                 :
                                                                 :
                                                                 .

    Loads of sysops have problems when they delete files, and forget to
     remove them from their dir-listings. Now, if YOU are one of them,
                    @{fg shine}   MGZDIRX @{fg text}is the tool for YOu!

  @{fg shine} MGZDIRX @{fg text}Scans through your dirs (selected in the cfgfile) and checks
   the dlpaths on your board if the files really excists. If they don't,
               @{fg shine} MGZDiRX @{fg text}removes the @{fg shine}FILE_ID @{fg text}from your dirs.

                            -magz of megastyle-

@endnode






